</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-1496_"><b>Utilise technology wisely</b> - Embrace technology that enhances patient care while ensuring it does not hinder personal interactions.
